alvo;<\/span><\/p>\n<p class=\"q\"><span class=\"v19_6_5\">que tu amor me libre de la muerte,<\/span><\/p>\n<p class=\"q\"><span class=\"v19_6_6\"><sup id=\"Ps.6.6\" class=\"v19_6_6\">6<\/sup>pues si uno muere pierde tu recuerdo;<\/span><\/p>\n<p class=\"q\"><span class=\"v19_6_6\">pues \u00bfqui\u00e9n puede alabarte<\/span><\/p>\n<p class=\"q\"><span class=\"v19_6_6\">en el reino de los muertos?<\/span><\/p>\n<p class=\"q\"><span class=\"v19_6_7\"><sup id=\"Ps.6.7\" class=\"v19_6_7\">7<\/sup>Estoy cansado de llorar,<\/span><\/p>\n<p class=\"q\"><span class=\"v19_6_7\">cada noche ba\u00f1o en l\u00e1grimas mi cama,<\/span><\/p>\n<p class=\"q\"><span class=\"v19_6_7\">con mi llanto inundo mi lecho.<\/span><\/p>\n<p class=\"q\"><span class=\"v19_6_8\"><sup id=\"Ps.6.8\" class=\"v19_6_8\">8<\/sup>Mis ojos se consumen de dolor,<\/span><\/p>\n<p class=\"q\"><span class=\"v19_6_8\">envejecen de tanta tristeza.<\/span><\/p>\n<p class=\"q\"><span class=\"v19_6_9\"><sup id=\"Ps.6.9\" class=\"v19_6_9\">9<\/sup>\u00a1Al\u00e9jense de m\u00ed, malvados,<\/span><\/p>\n<p class=\"q\"><span class=\"v19_6_9\">porque el Se\u00f1or ha escuchado mi llanto!<\/span><\/p>\n<p class=\"q\"><span class=\"v19_6_10\"><sup id=\"Ps.6.10\" class=\"v19_6_10\">10<\/sup>El Se\u00f1or ha escuchado mi ruego,<\/span><\/p>\n<p class=\"q\"><span class=\"v19_6_10\">el Se\u00f1or ha acogido mi s\u00faplica.<\/span><\/p>\n<p class=\"q\"><span class=\"v19_6_11\"><sup id=\"Ps.6.11\" class=\"v19_6_11\">11<\/sup>Mis enemigos, confusos y aterrados,<\/span><\/p>\n<p class=\"q\"><span class=\"v19_6_11\">huir\u00e1n, quedar\u00e1n de repente humillados.<\/span><\/p>\n<\/div>\n","chapter":"6","id":"spa-BHTI:Ps.6","osis_end":"spa-BHTI:Ps.6.11","order":"19006","link":"spa-BHTI\/Ps\/6","display":"SALMOS 6","book":{"version_id":"173","name":"SALMOS","abbr":"Ps","ord":"19","book_group_id":"0","testament":"OT","id":"spa-BHTI:Ps","osis_end":"spa-BHTI:Ps.150.6"},"version":{"auditid":"0","display_abbreviation":"BHTI","version":"spa-BHTI","id":"spa-BHTI","name":"La Biblia Hispanoamericana (Traducci\u00f3n Interconfesional, versi\u00f3n hispanoamericana)","short_desc":null,"description":null,"active":1,"active_api":0,"listed":1,"orderindex":"99","lang":"spa","lang_code":"ISO 639-3","copyright":"<p>La Biblia Hispanoamericana (BHTI) Traducci&#243;n Interconfesional versi&#243;n hispanoamericana Copyright &#169; Sociedad B&#237;blica de Espa&#241;a, 2011 Utilizada con permiso<\/p>","contact_url":"http:\/\/sociedadbiblica.org","audio":"NONE","sections":[{"version_id":"spa-BHTI","id":"OT","name":"Old Testament"},{"version_id":"spa-BHTI","id":"NT","name":"New Testament"}]},"audio":null,"prevChapterId":"spa-BHTI:Ps.5","nextChapterId":"spa-BHTI:Ps.7","footnotes":[],"crossreferences":[]},"prevChapter":{"auditid":"0","label":"","text":"<div id=\"Ps.4\" class=\"chapter\">\n<h3 class=\"ms2\">Salmo 4<\/h3>\n<h3 class=\"s1\">El Se\u00f1or me escucha cuando lo llamo<\/h3>\n<p class=\"q\"><span class=\"v19_4_1\"><sup id=\"Ps.4.1\" class=\"v19_4_1\">1<\/sup><span class=\"it\">Al maestro de coro; con instrumentos de cuerda. Salmo de David.<\/span><\/span><\/p>\n<p class=\"q\"><span class=\"v19_4_2\"><sup id=\"Ps.4.2\" class=\"v19_4_2\">2<\/sup>Resp\u00f3ndeme cuando te llame,<\/span><\/p>\n<p class=\"q\"><span class=\"v19_4_2\">t\u00fa, oh Dios, que eres mi defensor;<\/span><\/p>\n<p class=\"q\"><span class=\"v19_4_2\">t\u00fa que en la angustia me confortaste,<\/span><\/p>\n<p class=\"q\"><span class=\"v19_4_2\">api\u00e1date de m\u00ed, escucha mi oraci\u00f3n.<\/span><\/p>\n<p class=\"q\"><span class=\"v19_4_3\"><sup id=\"Ps.4.3\" class=\"v19_4_3\">3<\/sup>Y ustedes, \u00bfhasta cu\u00e1ndo me deshonrar\u00e1n,<\/span><\/p>\n<p class=\"q\"><span class=\"v19_4_3\">amar\u00e1n lo vano y desear\u00e1n lo falso? [<span class=\"it\">Pausa<\/span>]<\/span><\/p>\n<p class=\"q\"><span class=\"v19_4_4\"><sup id=\"Ps.4.4\" class=\"v19_4_4\">4<\/sup>Sepan que el Se\u00f1or enaltece al que es fiel,<\/span><\/p>\n<p class=\"q\"><span class=\"v19_4_4\">el Se\u00f1or me escucha cuando lo llamo.<\/span><\/p>\n<p class=\"q\"><span class=\"v19_4_5\"><sup id=\"Ps.4.5\" class=\"v19_4_5\">5<\/sup>Tiemblen y no pequen m\u00e1s,<\/span><\/p>\n<p class=\"q\"><span class=\"v19_4_5\">mediten en su lecho y guarden silencio; [<span class=\"it\">Pausa<\/span>]<\/span><\/p>\n<p class=\"q\"><span class=\"v19_4_6\"><sup id=\"Ps.4.6\" class=\"v19_4_6\">6<\/sup>ofrezcan sacrificios justos, conf\u00eden en el Se\u00f1or.<\/span><\/p>\n<p class=\"q\"><span class=\"v19_4_7\"><sup id=\"Ps.4.7\" class=\"v19_4_7\">7<\/sup>Muchos dicen: \u201c\u00bfQui\u00e9n nos mostrar\u00e1 el bien?\u201d.<\/span><\/p>\n<p class=\"q\"><span class=\"v19_4_7\">\u00a1Extiende sobre nosotros la luz de tu rostro, Se\u00f1or!<\/span><\/p>\n<p class=\"q\"><span class=\"v19_4_8\"><sup id=\"Ps.4.8\" class=\"v19_4_8\">8<\/sup>T\u00fa has alegrado mi coraz\u00f3n<\/span><\/p>\n<p class=\"q\"><span class=\"v19_4_8\">m\u00e1s que cuando abunda el trigo y el mosto.<\/span><\/p>\n<p class=\"q\"><span class=\"v19_4_9\"><sup id=\"Ps.4.9\" class=\"v19_4_9\">9<\/sup>En paz me acuesto y al instante me duermo<\/span><\/p>\n<p class=\"q\"><span class=\"v19_4_9\">porque s\u00f3lo t\u00fa, Se\u00f1or, me haces vivir tranquilo.<\/span><\/p>\n<\/div>\n","chapter":"4","id":"spa-BHTI:Ps.4","osis_end":"spa-BHTI:Ps.4.9","order":"19004","link":"spa-BHTI\/Ps\/4","display":"SALMOS 4","book":{"version_id":"173","name":"SALMOS","abbr":"Ps","ord":"19","book_group_id":"0","testament":"OT","id":"spa-BHTI:Ps","osis_end":"spa-BHTI:Ps.150.6"},"version":{"auditid":"0","display_abbreviation":"BHTI","version":"spa-BHTI","id":"spa-BHTI","name":"La Biblia Hispanoamericana (Traducci\u00f3n Interconfesional, versi\u00f3n hispanoamericana)","short_desc":null,"description":null,"active":1,"active_api":0,"listed":1,"orderindex":"99","lang":"spa","lang_code":"ISO 639-3","copyright":"<p>La Biblia Hispanoamericana (BHTI) Traducci&#243;n Interconfesional versi&#243;n h